						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1453 (1531 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Seems to record some provision for worship and offerings to the goddess Raṅganāyakī in the name of Ellamarasar. The details of the date viz. <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1453, ••••• , Vṛiśchika, ba. dvādaśī, Tuesday, Śōdi (Svāti)</hi> correspond to <hi rend="bold">1531 A.D., November 7, Tuesday; ·94; ·48.</hi> </p>						

